# HUD::DISPLAY_AMMO_THIS_FRAME

## Summary
Forces the display of ammo this frame if passed TRUE, forces OFF if passed FALSE

## Parameters
* **BOOL** value

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Must be called every frame
